Package net.casper.data.model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CBuilder
    Interface specifying elements required to build a CDataCacheContainer.
    CExporter
    Interface for exporting a Casper data container/rowset.
    CMarkedUpRowBean
    Classes implementing this interface can have their CMarkedUpRow set.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CDataCacheContainer
    The cache container serves as the implementation container class for 2-D data caches.
    CDataCacheDBAdapter
    Database adapter class.
    CDataCacheIndex
    This class represents an index on a particular column within a data cache.
    CDataCacheNonUniqueIndex
    A non-unique index, will construct a map of key values to a list of row object arrays.
    CDataComparator
    Data sorting functionality - implements comparator.
    CDataConstants
    Constants used internally by this data caching framework.
    CDataConverter
    Provides functionality to convert data from one type to another in the dataset implementation.
    CDataResultSet
    This is a JDBC ResultSet-compliant implementation of the casper rowset.
    CDataRow
    Represents a row of data.
    CDataRowSet
    A CDataRowSet represents one or more rows of data, stored in list format.
    CDataRowSetAggregator
    This class contains a limited set of aggregation functionality, which includes the following: (1) Sum, (2) WeightedSum, (3) Average, (4) WeightedAverage The rowset and column name upon which to aggregate are the two expected parameters for this aggregator
    CMarkedUpRow
    Represents a single CDataRow with its CRowMetaData.
    CRowMetaData
    Contains meta-data / configuration information for a "table" or "rowset" in cdataset.
    CTypes
    This class provides the various data types supported in data conversion.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CDataGridException
    Represents the generic exception for all data-grid based functionality
    CDataRuntimeException
    Exception with a dataset during runtime.
